              "description": "<p>Complete the following reflection form then proceed to the Semester 2 goals assignment. <a class=\"instructure_file_link instructure_scribd_file\" title=\"Individual Reflections(2).docx\" href=\"https://lms.theolympiaschools.edu.vn/courses/988/files/63956?verifier=I7K5IwdGXAvsQQXAeEhDSqPANw8Nl0Vb90TL7YaQ&amp;wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://lms.theolympiaschools.edu.vn/api/v1/courses/988/files/63956\" data-api-returntype=\"File\">Individual Reflections(2).docx</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>What did you learn this term? What was the most useful language or skill you have learned this term? What do you still need help with from this term? (ex. Grammar, vocabulary, reading, etc)</li>\n<li>What aspects of the course did you find easy? What aspects of the course you found difficult? What activities or assignments helped you learn the most/least? Why?&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Did you give your best effort this term? How can you prove to yourself, your peers, the teacher and your school that you understand our English course? (give examples and explanation)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>\n<p>What actions would you like to take in the next term in order to improve your academic performance?</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Write a minimum of 150 words and a maximum of 300 words for this part.</p>",
