              "id": 23635,
              "description": "<h4><strong>WRITING TASK 1</strong></h4>\n<p><strong><span>You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</span></strong></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 98.018%; height: 53px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 53px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 99.9081%; height: 53px;\">\n<p><strong>The table and chart show the Gross Regional Domestic Product (GRDP) in 2018 and the GRDP growth rate from 2017 to 2018 of five municipalities in Vietnam.</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span>Summarise the information by selecting and reporting the main features, and&nbsp;</span><span>make comparisons where relevant.</span><br><span>Write at least 150 words.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>GRDP of five municipalities in Vietnam in 2018 (billion VND)</strong></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 35.6433%; height: 225px; border-color: #ced4d9; border-style: groove;\" width=\"404\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.5382%; height: 44px;\">Hanoi</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.3699%; height: 44px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 706,495</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.5382%; height: 44px;\">Ho Chi Minh</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.3699%; height: 44px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1,331,440</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.5382%; height: 44px;\">Haiphong</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.3699%; height: 44px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 195,540</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.5382%; height: 44px;\">Danang</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.3699%; height: 44px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 90,023</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.5382%; height: 44px;\">Can Tho</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.3699%; height: 44px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 103,143</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img id=\"160002568\" src=\"https://lms.theolympiaschools.edu.vn/courses/988/files/65308/preview?verifier=MNwQAWErAEwLPXUIzmUaf2KPpABAdKLEle0VcKwp\" alt=\"GDP_chart.png\" width=\"840\" height=\"514\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://lms.theolympiaschools.edu.vn/api/v1/courses/988/files/65308\" data-api-returntype=\"File\"></p>",
